You're very polite.

54:59.830 --> 55:02.867
♪ Shoo-shoo-shoo,
shoo-shoo-shoo-shoo... ♪

55:04.435 --> 55:06.471
You're a good person.

55:22.687 --> 55:24.555
- Okay.
- Listen,

55:24.555 --> 55:26.991
you guys met on some kind
of message board, right?

55:26.991 --> 55:28.993
You're having a shared delusion.

55:28.993 --> 55:31.328
That's a uniquely 21st-century
health crisis.

55:31.328 --> 55:32.730
It is real.

55:32.730 --> 55:35.065
You're in an echo chamber,
you know that, right?

55:35.933 --> 55:38.703
You got online,
and you found random people

55:38.703 --> 55:42.172
who had random visions
and you took that as evidence.

55:42.172 --> 55:43.874
Remember the guy
who shot up three people

55:43.874 --> 55:45.275
in an Army base in Louisiana?

55:45.275 --> 55:47.077
He was part of an online group
like yours.

55:47.077 --> 55:49.279
They posted videos about
how the shadow government

55:49.279 --> 55:52.016
was stalking them
and using mind control weapons

55:52.016 --> 55:54.652
in an attempt to destroy
their lives.

55:55.420 --> 55:56.887
We found each other online

55:56.887 --> 55:58.656
because we said
we had the same visions.

55:58.656 --> 56:00.525
Remember what
you did at Thanksgiving?

56:00.525 --> 56:03.561
And then we decided
to meet on the boardwalk.

56:03.561 --> 56:06.564
You're gonna do that if I nod.

56:06.564 --> 56:09.099
Okay, let's continue.

56:21.446 --> 56:24.915
You have the opportunity
to choose.

56:27.785 --> 56:29.253
I don't mean to rush you,

56:29.253 --> 56:33.090
but we're gonna ask for your
decisions very fast now.

56:35.593 --> 56:37.327
I'm gonna be straight up.

56:40.064 --> 56:41.799
I'm the next one to go.

56:44.001 --> 56:45.703
I'm counting on you, man.

56:45.703 --> 56:48.506
You're, like, my last hope here.

56:48.506 --> 56:50.140
Adriane,

56:50.140 --> 56:52.510
you can walk out of here
right now.

56:52.510 --> 56:55.446
Just walk out and see,
nothing will happen.

56:55.446 --> 56:57.715
None of this can stop
until you make a choice.

56:57.715 --> 56:58.949
Don't you get that already?

57:01.051 --> 57:03.220
You think I want to be here?

57:03.220 --> 57:05.490
I'm just some fucking cook.

57:06.857 --> 57:08.526
I didn't tell you at first,

57:08.526 --> 57:11.428
but I have a son.

57:11.428 --> 57:13.531
I didn't want to speak
his name, but...

57:13.531 --> 57:16.200
here I am, begging you to do
what has to be done

57:16.200 --> 57:19.236
because if you don't,
my son is gonna die.

57:20.370 --> 57:22.807
Over the last few days,
I've had to watch him die

57:22.807 --> 57:24.609
over and over and over again.

57:24.609 --> 57:27.111
I've watched my little boy
burned alive

57:27.111 --> 57:29.547
as I held him in my arms.

57:30.347 --> 57:31.882
Everything was burning.

57:31.882 --> 57:35.052
I can't get the sound
of his screams out of my head,

57:35.052 --> 57:37.187
even right now, so...

57:37.187 --> 57:40.658
as a mother, believe me
when I tell you

57:40.658 --> 57:42.993
that this is really happening.

57:44.529 --> 57:45.963
And it's up to you.

57:45.963 --> 57:47.865
What exactly did you guys see?

57:47.865 --> 57:50.568
Stop talking to him.

57:50.568 --> 57:52.837
He doesn't believe you.

57:52.837 --> 57:55.039
None of us believe you.

57:55.039 --> 57:57.074
Let your time run out.

57:57.074 --> 58:00.210
We're not gonna do
what you want us to do.

58:07.284 --> 58:10.087
His name is Charlie.

58:13.223 --> 58:15.526
He likes pancakes.

58:37.615 --> 58:39.249
Very well.

58:41.586 --> 58:44.989
Close your eyes
and cover your ears.

58:46.891 --> 58:48.959
You don't have to do this.

58:48.959 --> 58:50.327
You guys are delusional.

58:50.327 --> 58:51.862
You are part of a suicide cult.

58:51.862 --> 58:53.731
Can't you see that?

59:01.572 --> 59:02.940
Stop!

59:02.940 --> 59:04.909
Please stop this!

59:41.545 --> 59:45.049
A part of humanity
has been judged.

1:00:08.338 --> 1:00:10.074
I'll move her
into the other room

1:00:10.074 --> 1:00:11.876
so they don't have to see her.

1:00:30.627 --> 1:00:33.563
Hundreds of thousands of people
are going to die now.

1:00:34.965 --> 1:00:37.668
We've unleashed a second plague.

1:00:39.937 --> 1:00:41.739
Bullshit.

1:00:43.908 --> 1:00:46.510
Sabrina, put on the TV, please.

1:00:54.651 --> 1:00:56.420
There have also been
new developments

1:00:56.420 --> 1:00:58.322
with the novel X-Nine virus,

1:00:58.322 --> 1:01:01.826
which is proving particularly
fatal to children.

1:01:01.826 --> 1:01:04.094
The X-Nine virus
is highly transmittable

1:01:04.094 --> 1:01:06.630
amongst children
aged ten and under.

1:01:06.630 --> 1:01:08.632
These outbreaks seem
to be originating

1:01:08.632 --> 1:01:11.869
in three distinct pockets
of the world:

1:01:11.869 --> 1:01:13.704
Cape Town, Suffolk, England,

1:01:13.704 --> 1:01:16.573
and outside Nashville
in Tennessee.

1:01:16.573 --> 1:01:19.243
Lockdowns in these areas
have already begun

1:01:19.243 --> 1:01:21.145
as numbers rise along with fear

1:01:21.145 --> 1:01:23.347
for the safety
of those infected.

1:01:23.347 --> 1:01:25.816
Numerous public schools
have been suspended

1:01:25.816 --> 1:01:27.184
with some being converted

1:01:27.184 --> 1:01:29.887
into makeshift
quarantine facilities.

1:01:29.887 --> 1:01:32.356
While there is hope that
the virus will be contained

1:01:32.356 --> 1:01:33.758
to the geographical pockets
in question...

1:01:33.758 --> 1:01:35.692
I think
I saw something, Andrew.

1:01:35.692 --> 1:01:37.661
...these communities
are trapped in lockdown.

1:01:37.661 --> 1:01:39.163
What?

1:01:39.163 --> 1:01:40.798
What are you saying?

1:01:40.798 --> 1:01:42.699
I think I saw a person.

1:01:42.699 --> 1:01:45.202
Or a figure.

1:01:45.202 --> 1:01:47.537
Turn the TV off.

1:01:48.572 --> 1:01:51.275
Where'd you see a figure?

1:01:52.109 --> 1:01:54.044
In the light behind you.

1:01:54.044 --> 1:01:56.446
In the reflection in the mirror.

1:01:57.247 --> 1:01:59.649
When you were standing
behind Redmond.

1:01:59.649 --> 1:02:01.819
Right before you struck him.

1:02:03.120 --> 1:02:05.689
Eric, look at me.

1:02:07.457 --> 1:02:09.359
You have a severe concussion.

1:02:09.359 --> 1:02:10.761
She even told you

1:02:10.761 --> 1:02:12.296
you would be extremely
sensitive to light.

1:02:12.296 --> 1:02:15.465
We're under extreme stress here.

1:02:15.465 --> 1:02:18.035
I need you to listen
to the words I'm saying.

1:02:18.035 --> 1:02:20.637
Breathe in for a second, okay?

1:02:26.043 --> 1:02:28.312
I've been reading about
these X-Nine cases

1:02:28.312 --> 1:02:30.380
for months already,
you know that.

1:02:30.380 --> 1:02:32.917
It isn't a fucking plague.

1:02:32.917 --> 1:02:34.684
It's a news report.

1:02:34.684 --> 1:02:37.021
They all knew about it
before they showed up here

1:02:37.021 --> 1:02:39.689
and knowingly made it
a part of their narrative.

1:02:39.689 --> 1:02:43.327
And this guy has been checking
his watch all morning

1:02:43.327 --> 1:02:44.862
just like yesterday.

1:02:44.862 --> 1:02:46.630
- Come on, Andrew.
- All four of you have watches.

1:02:46.630 --> 1:02:48.365
What, you just showed up here
like that? No.

1:02:48.365 --> 1:02:50.234
You knew you were coming
at this particular cabin

1:02:50.234 --> 1:02:52.769
where cell reception
wouldn't exist.

1:02:52.769 --> 1:02:54.704
Did you see the banner
at the bottom of the screen?

1:02:54.704 --> 1:02:56.406
It isn't live.
It's preprogramming.

1:02:56.406 --> 1:02:57.774
It's a TV show.

1:02:57.774 --> 1:02:59.376
Leonard, Sabrina,

1:02:59.376 --> 1:03:01.145
all of them knew
this X-Nine show would be on

1:03:01.145 --> 1:03:02.847
- and at what time.
- Andrew, this virus

1:03:02.847 --> 1:03:04.514
- is gonna spread everywhere.
- If you...

1:03:04.514 --> 1:03:06.951
It's a fucking
preprogrammed show!

1:03:07.751 --> 1:03:09.719
They knew this virus show
would be on at this time,

1:03:09.719 --> 1:03:11.355
just like they knew
the Alaskan earthquake

1:03:11.355 --> 1:03:13.290
and the tsunami warning
had already happened

1:03:13.290 --> 1:03:15.525
before they showed up here.

1:03:22.499 --> 1:03:24.902
I'm clearheaded now.

1:03:27.938 --> 1:03:29.974
Always together.

1:03:34.211 --> 1:03:37.014
You don't talk to him
from now on. You talk to me.

1:03:44.554 --> 1:03:46.023
I want to watch
Paddington and Chloe now!

1:03:46.023 --> 1:03:48.025
I want to watch
Paddington and Chloe!

1:03:48.025 --> 1:03:49.826
Wen.

1:03:51.028 --> 1:03:52.562
I want to watch a cartoon now!

1:03:52.562 --> 1:03:54.198
- Wen, okay.

1:03:54.198 --> 1:03:55.866
We're gonna count down from
five together, and we're not

1:03:55.866 --> 1:03:57.401
- gonna yell anymore, okay?
- I want to watch it now!

1:03:57.401 --> 1:03:59.169
Wen. Five...

1:03:59.169 --> 1:04:01.005
I want to watch Paddington
and Chloe now! -...four...

1:04:01.005 --> 1:04:02.439
- Okay, let's try this again.
