1:04:17.487 --> 1:04:19.323
No! No, I don't believe you!

1:04:19.323 --> 1:04:21.926
- Eric, please. Please stop...
- No. No, no. Back away from me.

1:04:21.926 --> 1:04:25.029
Don't you look at me.
Don't you look at my daughter!

1:04:25.029 --> 1:04:26.496
Look, you don't
understand what you're doing!

1:04:26.496 --> 1:04:27.965
I don't fucking
believe you! No! -Please!

1:04:27.965 --> 1:04:31.001
No! No, I don't believe
a word you say! Fuck you!

1:04:35.973 --> 1:04:37.407
- Andrew.

1:04:47.651 --> 1:04:49.819
I hit you in the knee
just so you wouldn't run away.

1:04:49.819 --> 1:04:52.722
This is triage,
like in an emergency room.

1:04:52.722 --> 1:04:54.758
We have to make the decision
to save the most lives.

1:04:54.758 --> 1:04:56.193
We have to help each other.

1:04:56.193 --> 1:04:58.929
We have to help each other.

1:05:11.441 --> 1:05:12.977
- Open up!

1:05:12.977 --> 1:05:15.179
Andrew, listen to me!

1:05:15.179 --> 1:05:17.047
Andrew.

1:05:21.986 --> 1:05:23.120
Come on.

1:05:24.521 --> 1:05:26.656
Please! Come out!

1:05:26.656 --> 1:05:28.025
- Come on.

1:05:29.259 --> 1:05:30.961
Stay away from me.

1:05:30.961 --> 1:05:33.097
Stay away from me!
I will kill you!

1:05:33.097 --> 1:05:34.631
Stay away from me!

1:05:40.870 --> 1:05:42.572
Please stop!

1:05:49.579 --> 1:05:50.880
Leave whatever you're going for,

1:05:50.880 --> 1:05:54.151
get out of the car
and come inside!

1:05:54.985 --> 1:05:57.487
I don't want to have
to hurt you!

1:05:58.255 --> 1:06:00.424
- Come back inside!

1:06:00.424 --> 1:06:02.059
Now!

1:06:02.059 --> 1:06:03.960
We don't have time for this!
Please!

1:06:03.960 --> 1:06:05.862
Andrew, listen.

1:06:13.670 --> 1:06:15.972
Now, you listen to me,
you crazy fucking bitch.

1:06:16.806 --> 1:06:18.675
You drop that thing
and back the fuck up.

1:06:18.675 --> 1:06:21.778
Okay. Okay.

1:06:21.778 --> 1:06:23.813
- Back the fuck up!
- Okay, okay!

1:06:25.282 --> 1:06:27.984
- Keep going!
- Okay, okay.

1:06:27.984 --> 1:06:29.153
Move!

1:06:29.153 --> 1:06:30.720
Breathe.

1:06:35.292 --> 1:06:37.694
Stop. Stop!

1:06:47.271 --> 1:06:50.074
Fuck. Fuck.

1:07:05.889 --> 1:07:06.890
Stay back!

1:07:06.890 --> 1:07:08.325
I believe you were chosen because

1:07:08.325 --> 1:07:10.927
your family's love
for each other is so pure.

1:07:10.927 --> 1:07:12.529
I know you've been through
a lot,

1:07:12.529 --> 1:07:13.963
and people haven't been fair
to you.

1:07:18.001 --> 1:07:20.904
Drop the weapon
and move away from Eric,

1:07:20.904 --> 1:07:23.973
or I'll show you I was chosen
to put a bullet in your head.

1:07:23.973 --> 1:07:27.377
Drop it now, Leonard,
or I'll kill you!

1:07:27.377 --> 1:07:29.246
You're dooming us all, Andrew.

1:07:29.246 --> 1:07:31.815
You're dooming your husband,
you're dooming your daughter...

1:07:31.815 --> 1:07:33.350
I'm done with you!

1:07:33.350 --> 1:07:35.652
I'm not listening to another
goddamn word you say!

1:07:38.155 --> 1:07:40.090
It's time
for the next sacrifice.

1:07:41.158 --> 1:07:43.360
Are you willing
to make a choice?

1:07:43.360 --> 1:07:45.162
You're crazy.

1:07:46.096 --> 1:07:49.966
I'm taking my family,
and I'm leaving.

1:07:52.936 --> 1:07:54.604
- Andrew!

1:08:08.418 --> 1:08:10.620
You have a temper.

1:08:10.620 --> 1:08:14.458
Not in a scary way, just...

1:08:14.458 --> 1:08:16.326
It's there.

1:08:16.326 --> 1:08:18.995
You're uptight.

1:08:18.995 --> 1:08:20.964
You can...

1:08:20.964 --> 1:08:23.867
suck the life
out of any situation.

1:08:23.867 --> 1:08:26.503
Hey, we said you have
to qualify things.

1:08:26.503 --> 1:08:27.937
I'm sorry. You...

1:08:27.937 --> 1:08:30.540
You suck the life
out of some situations.

1:08:31.708 --> 1:08:33.777
I'll accept that.

1:08:33.777 --> 1:08:36.346
It's not a bad list.

1:08:36.346 --> 1:08:39.649
I think most parents would have
a worse list than that.

1:08:40.450 --> 1:08:42.786
I can't believe
we're actually gonna do this.

1:08:42.786 --> 1:08:45.789
I have never,

1:08:45.789 --> 1:08:48.692
for one second of my life,

1:08:48.692 --> 1:08:51.027
ever doubted loving you.

1:08:52.028 --> 1:08:55.165
The kid'll be washed in that
every day.

1:08:55.165 --> 1:08:58.668
How is it you can say stuff
like that out of nowhere?

1:08:58.668 --> 1:09:01.205
Can you guys keep it down?

1:09:03.207 --> 1:09:05.108
Were we being loud?

1:09:05.108 --> 1:09:08.645
I'm trying to have a drink
with my friends.

1:09:09.546 --> 1:09:11.815
Oh, we were being too loud?

1:09:12.749 --> 1:09:15.084
Is that what it is?

1:09:16.386 --> 1:09:19.789
Get your drunk ass
back to your seat.

1:09:20.557 --> 1:09:22.892
Fuck you.

1:09:26.463 --> 1:09:28.298
You shouldn't provoke them.

1:09:28.298 --> 1:09:29.533
I wasn't provoking...

1:09:29.533 --> 1:09:31.601
Oh, my God! What the fuck?

1:09:31.601 --> 1:09:33.136
What the fuck?
Andrew, are you okay?

1:09:33.136 --> 1:09:34.538
- Andrew.

1:09:34.538 --> 1:09:36.406
Oh, my God! What the fuck!

1:09:37.607 --> 1:09:39.643
Somebody call an ambulance!

1:09:39.643 --> 1:09:41.645
Andrew! Andrew, look at me.

1:09:41.645 --> 1:09:43.447
Andrew, look at me.
Are you okay?

1:09:43.447 --> 1:09:44.981
Open your eyes. Open your eyes.

1:09:44.981 --> 1:09:47.717
Can you hear me? Andrew!

1:10:09.172 --> 1:10:11.908
All right, so what
you got here is an HK P30.

1:10:11.908 --> 1:10:15.879
German engineered, very light,
very easy to handle.

1:10:16.980 --> 1:10:19.616
Um, pretty much good
for any scenario.

1:10:19.616 --> 1:10:21.184
Carry, home protection.

1:10:21.184 --> 1:10:22.919
Screw 'em, right?

1:10:27.491 --> 1:10:29.359
I'll take it.

1:10:43.640 --> 1:10:45.809
No, Leonard.

1:10:49.245 --> 1:10:51.981
Are you willing
to make a sacrifice?

1:10:53.049 --> 1:10:54.784
No more, you bastard.

1:10:58.221 --> 1:11:01.190
A part of humanity
has been judged.

1:11:16.172 --> 1:11:19.042
The four of us
can't make this decision.

1:11:19.042 --> 1:11:20.944
It's got to be your choice.

1:11:20.944 --> 1:11:23.112
Shut your mouth.

1:11:25.815 --> 1:11:27.351
Keep an eye on Leonard.

1:11:28.885 --> 1:11:30.987
Yell if he does anything.

1:12:05.589 --> 1:12:07.857
It's O'Bannon.

1:12:17.801 --> 1:12:19.168
They were here to torture us.

1:12:19.168 --> 1:12:20.970
We don't know why
we were chosen.

1:12:20.970 --> 1:12:23.106
Don't say another word
of your horseshit!

1:12:23.106 --> 1:12:27.143
None of this is real,
and you were targeting us!

1:12:27.143 --> 1:12:29.145
I always look for motive, Leonard.

1:12:29.145 --> 1:12:30.847
How about a crazy bigot

1:12:30.847 --> 1:12:32.882
meets a bartender
from a bar somewhere,

1:12:32.882 --> 1:12:35.184
and they find a woman
from a small town

1:12:35.184 --> 1:12:37.454
who has extreme
religious beliefs.

1:12:37.454 --> 1:12:38.555
That's not true.

1:12:38.555 --> 1:12:39.989
Then they come across
a young woman

1:12:39.989 --> 1:12:41.658
who can be persuaded
of anything.

1:12:41.658 --> 1:12:44.260
I didn't believe for a second
that Adriane had a kid, Leonard!

1:12:45.562 --> 1:12:48.932
Now, I'm not a murderer
like you guys,

1:12:48.932 --> 1:12:51.034
so I'm gonna lock you
in that bathroom.

1:12:53.269 --> 1:12:55.171
They slashed our tires,

1:12:55.171 --> 1:12:59.409
but they must've come
in a... a truck or a vehicle.

1:13:00.944 --> 1:13:03.379
We have to get to that vehicle.

1:13:03.379 --> 1:13:06.115
You're wrong about all of us.

1:13:06.115 --> 1:13:07.917
Now get in that bathroom, Leonard.

1:13:07.917 --> 1:13:09.252
And make no mistake,

1:13:09.252 --> 1:13:12.288
I will fucking kill you
if I have to.

1:13:20.329 --> 1:13:22.165
We need something
to tie the doorknob to.

1:13:22.165 --> 1:13:23.967
The lamp.

1:13:23.967 --> 1:13:25.669
Here.

1:13:30.507 --> 1:13:32.776
Okay. Come on. Come on.

1:13:36.780 --> 1:13:38.281
He broke the window.

1:13:38.281 --> 1:13:40.149
He got out.

1:13:42.218 --> 1:13:43.853
He's gonna come get us!

1:13:48.592 --> 1:13:51.194
He's gonna get to the car
before us.

1:13:51.194 --> 1:13:52.696
He could be outside and hurt us.

1:13:52.696 --> 1:13:55.231
We have to make sure
he's in the bathroom.

1:13:56.533 --> 1:13:58.201
Leonard?

1:14:00.837 --> 1:14:04.373
If I open this door and
I see you, I will shoot you.

1:14:07.410 --> 1:14:09.245
Leonard!

1:15:05.802 --> 1:15:06.903
Get off him!

1:15:19.448 --> 1:15:22.986
Fuck. Fuck.

1:15:29.959 --> 1:15:31.427
I thought you wouldn't kill us.

1:15:31.427 --> 1:15:33.262
I won't.

1:15:33.262 --> 1:15:34.964
But I will shoot you in the leg

1:15:34.964 --> 1:15:36.766
to keep you from leaving
this cabin.

1:15:36.766 --> 1:15:38.768
Turn on the TV
if you want to be convinced.

1:15:39.969 --> 1:15:41.304
You'll see that everything

1:15:41.304 --> 1:15:42.972
I said was gonna happen
has happened.

1:15:42.972 --> 1:15:45.074
No one's gonna do what you
say... -More terrifying images

1:15:45.074 --> 1:15:47.076
as we see yet another
passenger aircraft

1:15:47.076 --> 1:15:49.278
- plummet to the ground.

1:15:49.278 --> 1:15:51.781
- Eric, what are you doing?

1:15:54.017 --> 1:15:55.451
Why did you turn it on?

1:15:55.451 --> 1:15:57.186
Local and
international governments

1:15:57.186 --> 1:15:59.255
are investigating whether
there's any correlation

1:15:59.255 --> 1:16:01.224
between the crashes.

1:16:01.224 --> 1:16:03.492
We have yet to receive
death tolls

1:16:03.492 --> 1:16:06.630
or receive any statements
from the airlines.

1:16:21.210 --> 1:16:23.212
You said it wasn't real.

1:16:49.438 --> 1:16:51.307
The skies will fall
and crash to the earth

1:16:51.307 --> 1:16:53.342
like pieces of glass.

1:16:53.342 --> 1:16:56.713
And God's fingers
will scorch the earth...

1:16:56.713 --> 1:17:00.349
and an everlasting darkness
will descend over humanity.

1:17:01.584 --> 1:17:03.486
We now have confirmation

1:17:03.486 --> 1:17:07.556
of as many as 700 airplanes
having crashed without warning,

1:17:07.556 --> 1:17:09.625
without issuing distress calls,

1:17:09.625 --> 1:17:11.895
amid fears
and increasing speculation

1:17:11.895 --> 1:17:14.764
there may have been
a coordinated cyberattack...

1:17:14.764 --> 1:17:17.033
That terrorist stuff
has nothing to do with this.

1:17:17.033 --> 1:17:18.434
I've heard this before.

1:17:18.434 --> 1:17:20.503
TSA has yet
to issue a statement.

1:17:20.503 --> 1:17:23.807
Airports around the globe
are canceling flights.

1:17:25.074 --> 1:17:27.410
- It is hard...
- It is hard...

1:17:27.410 --> 1:17:29.145
- Excuse me.
- Excuse me.

1:17:29.145 --> 1:17:32.281
It is hard to describe
the images that we are seeing.

1:17:32.281 --> 1:17:36.385
They fill us with disquietude
and horror.

1:17:36.385 --> 1:17:38.688
We are witnessing
a collective tragedy

1:17:38.688 --> 1:17:41.891
unfathomable
only moments before.

1:17:44.160 --> 1:17:46.562
We are getting word
of more airline...

1:17:47.330 --> 1:17:49.699
How the fuck did you know
what she was gonna say?

1:17:49.699 --> 1:17:53.369
Is this some closed-circuit TV?
Did you guys pump this in?

1:17:53.369 --> 1:17:56.105
Maybe the truth is...

1:17:56.105 --> 1:17:57.540
is that the end was happening

1:17:57.540 --> 1:18:00.744
long before
we got to this cabin.

1:18:00.744 --> 1:18:04.180
And what we're seeing now
isn't the fireworks.

1:18:04.180 --> 1:18:07.050
It's just the final
flickering sparks.

1:18:07.817 --> 1:18:10.119
I don't know
what's going on here,

1:18:10.119 --> 1:18:12.789
but where are the keys
to the truck you guys came in?

1:18:12.789 --> 1:18:13.990
Andrew.

1:18:13.990 --> 1:18:18.161
I'm taking my family...
and we're leaving.

1:18:19.462 --> 1:18:24.300
Do you really think that
everything that happened today,

1:18:24.300 --> 1:18:26.903
everything we've seen...

1:18:28.437 --> 1:18:31.574
Do you really think
it's all just a coincidence?

1:18:32.575 --> 1:18:33.977
Yes.

1:18:33.977 --> 1:18:35.912
I think it's all a coincidence.

1:18:36.746 --> 1:18:39.515
Some horrible,
unexplainable coincidence.

1:18:39.515 --> 1:18:41.184
Or it has to be a trick.

1:18:41.184 --> 1:18:43.186
I have to believe that!

1:18:44.020 --> 1:18:46.455
You already don't believe that.

1:18:48.424 --> 1:18:50.760
I know when someone's lying.

1:18:51.895 --> 1:18:53.562
Eric...

1:18:53.562 --> 1:18:55.865
let's go.

1:18:57.566 --> 1:19:01.537
Let's get out of here
and never come back.

1:19:03.072 --> 1:19:04.974
Don't listen to Leonard anymore.

1:19:20.423 --> 1:19:23.626
Can everyone come out
onto the back deck now?

1:19:25.528 --> 1:19:28.564
I'd like to do
this last part outside.

1:19:34.370 --> 1:19:36.739
What are you doing
with that, Leonard?

1:19:39.242 --> 1:19:42.611
When I'm gone, you'll only have
minutes to stop everything.

1:19:42.611 --> 1:19:44.948
After that, it'll be too late.

1:19:46.582 --> 1:19:48.151
Will all the children die?

1:19:48.151 --> 1:19:50.753
Wen, I want you to take
your music and your headphones

1:19:50.753 --> 1:19:52.956
and go to that tree house
that we climbed in.

1:19:52.956 --> 1:19:56.092
Put your music on until
one of us comes to get you.

1:19:56.092 --> 1:19:58.394
Do what Daddy says, okay?

1:20:01.564 --> 1:20:02.932
I love you, chicken.

1:20:02.932 --> 1:20:04.600
I love you, too.

1:20:05.935 --> 1:20:07.871
Go. Go.

1:20:09.072 --> 1:20:11.774
Nothing can happen
to the three of us.

1:20:11.774 --> 1:20:13.442
You'll be okay.

1:20:16.312 --> 1:20:19.715
The worst thing about
the visions was the screaming.

1:20:21.084 --> 1:20:23.452
I could hear everyone screaming.

1:20:24.653 --> 1:20:26.089
And I knew
when the visions ended,

1:20:26.089 --> 1:20:30.793
the screaming was just
gonna go on and on.

1:20:36.065 --> 1:20:39.035
You know what I loved most
about teaching kids?

1:20:40.336 --> 1:20:42.671
They believe everything you say.

1:20:43.606 --> 1:20:45.708
So you have to be careful.

1:20:46.475 --> 1:20:50.746
Say only what you know,
what you know to be true.

1:20:51.614 --> 1:20:54.017
It's a big responsibility.

1:20:56.685 --> 1:20:59.088
Maybe one of the kids I taught

1:20:59.088 --> 1:21:01.925
will do something great
for the world.

1:21:01.925 --> 1:21:04.027
What do you think?

1:21:08.097 --> 1:21:10.533
Please...

1:21:10.533 --> 1:21:16.572
my new friends, Eric, Andrew...

1:21:19.808 --> 1:21:24.213
...will you make a choice
and save the world?

1:21:35.691 --> 1:21:37.961
All of humanity has been judged.

1:22:42.625 --> 1:22:45.094
We still have a few minutes,
he said.

1:22:47.463 --> 1:22:48.697
Eric.

1:22:48.697 --> 1:22:51.434
There was something
in the light.

1:22:51.434 --> 1:22:53.169
A figure.

1:22:59.042 --> 1:23:01.510
And I feel it now.

1:23:08.417 --> 1:23:10.486
I believe you.

1:23:12.255 --> 1:23:14.890
Let's the three of us leave.

1:23:19.795 --> 1:23:22.665
Maybe this is the way
it's always been.

1:23:24.267 --> 1:23:27.803
Maybe families have been
deciding this all through time.

1:23:29.572 --> 1:23:32.041
Let's just walk the earth, then.

1:23:33.242 --> 1:23:35.044
The three of us.

1:23:35.044 --> 1:23:37.913
What kind of life is that
for Wen?

1:23:40.483 --> 1:23:42.585
Andrew, this wasn't
a home invasion.

1:23:44.320 --> 1:23:45.821
They didn't target us.

1:23:45.821 --> 1:23:48.724
They came here
to spend time with us...

1:23:50.493 --> 1:23:53.229
...for us to get to know them.

1:23:53.229 --> 1:23:56.099
They remind us of all aspects
of humanity.

1:23:57.100 --> 1:23:59.802
Redmond, malice.

1:23:59.802 --> 1:24:02.571
Adriane, nurturing.

1:24:02.571 --> 1:24:05.341
Sabrina, healing.

1:24:05.341 --> 1:24:07.410
Leonard, guidance.

1:24:08.177 --> 1:24:10.779
They're the Four Horsemen
of the Apocalypse.

1:24:10.779 --> 1:24:12.481
I believe we had
to see them die.

1:24:12.481 --> 1:24:14.617
We had to feel their loss.

1:24:15.384 --> 1:24:17.520
Why us?

1:24:18.521 --> 1:24:20.556
We're nothing special.

1:24:20.556 --> 1:24:23.192
Because I know what I felt when
we saw Wen in that orphanage

1:24:23.192 --> 1:24:25.628
and we were together
for the first time.

1:24:26.429 --> 1:24:27.963
It's our decision.

1:24:30.799 --> 1:24:33.068
It's our fucking decision?

1:24:35.104 --> 1:24:38.341
We're supposed to give up
our love for them?

1:24:38.341 --> 1:24:40.075
It's a sacrifice, Andrew.

1:24:40.075 --> 1:24:41.877
That we would be willing
to give up

1:24:41.877 --> 1:24:43.879
something so beautiful to us
for everyone else.

1:24:43.879 --> 1:24:46.182
- They're not worth it!

1:24:46.182 --> 1:24:47.450
They hate us, Eric.

1:24:47.450 --> 1:24:49.051
They hate that we exist.

1:24:49.051 --> 1:24:50.753
- They're just scared.

1:24:50.753 --> 1:24:52.054
Like all of us.

1:24:52.054 --> 1:24:53.489
They're monsters.

1:24:53.489 --> 1:24:55.291
They destroy everything.

1:24:55.291 --> 1:24:56.659
They hurt each other.

1:24:56.659 --> 1:24:57.960
You're not just a prosecutor.

1:24:57.960 --> 1:24:59.395
You know there's something
to defend.

1:24:59.395 --> 1:25:00.963
That's where your anger
comes from, Andrew.

1:25:01.997 --> 1:25:02.798
Kill me.

1:25:02.798 --> 1:25:04.633
No, sweetheart.

1:25:05.968 --> 1:25:07.870
We're running out of time.

1:25:07.870 --> 1:25:09.838
Maybe I saw a figure,
maybe I just made it up,

1:25:09.838 --> 1:25:11.274
but it's giving me peace.

1:25:11.274 --> 1:25:13.209
My mind is set in its truth.

1:25:14.477 --> 1:25:16.445
I won't be scared.

1:25:16.445 --> 1:25:17.580
You gotta do it now.

1:25:17.580 --> 1:25:19.047
We're out of time. All of us.

1:25:19.047 --> 1:25:20.949
I don't believe in them, Eric.

1:25:20.949 --> 1:25:22.451
I do.

1:25:23.486 --> 1:25:25.454
Do it while I'm thinking
the most beautiful thought

